HEADWORD: Kranging hook
<hw>Krang"ing hook`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Whaling)</fld>
<def>A hook for holding the blubber while cutting it away.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>cranging hook</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
